{"tid":296830,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"想買電子鋼琴 Budget 4000-5000","createTime":"2017-06-25T03:11:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T09:10:21.000Z","uid":66659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ab4ba87ce80d555cf93b891be2569d02010d5a7","tid":296830,"uid":66659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:11:09.000Z","msg":"新手想買鋼琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主要練下鋼琴書D歌， 都會彈下流行曲<br />\n要求如下：<br />\n1. 唔要大大部果D，要果D有架橕住到半個人咁高D,好似下面張圖咁:<br />\n<img src=\"http://a.ecimg.tw/items/AIAH06A30630224/000001_1478098237.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa.ecimg.tw%2Fitems%2FAIAH06A30630224%2F000001_1478098237.jpg&h=a1f82a91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.有踏板<br />\n3. 可以插耳機入去，費是嘈親人<br />\n<br />\n另外以下果的係希望有嘅功能，冇都冇所謂：<br />\n1. 可以同電腦連接，錄音<br />\n2. 可以output 駁入喇叭到（3.5 mm or Aux in)<br />\n<br />\n新手咩都唔知價，如果覺得我出價低請屌得細力D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6969274f701e939a56aa7c5f870a9ad3aaa9851","tid":296830,"uid":66659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:12:55.000Z","msg":"Sor 鳩淨係up咗琴架張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ， 但係應該都知我講邊隻琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d244dc3c4241f1d6cebacf129a06ee2cc3d33bc8","tid":296830,"uid":66659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:20:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935f0e62edbda83b774abfbe911f9ecb87a957ed","tid":296830,"uid":66659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:32:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2691ace6aec44198c059afa6975599c0bd7772bc","tid":296830,"uid":82068,"like":