>\n彈電子琴手感唔同好易彈壞手<br />\n一係儲多d買R牌數碼琴啦</blockquote><br />\n要多幾錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新手想彈但係冇位擺琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前有去琴房練，但係覺得好貴先想買琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你同我個時一樣 <br />\n我個時日日收工成身汗咁走去琴行日日鍊兩個鐘<br />\n之後諗左好耐下定決心就去買左部Yamaha u1<br />\nR牌琴你預起碼一萬尾到 你可以去柏斯睇下試下琴試下聲同手感 鑽石山荷里活個間都幾大下 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e1ac6f69ba057a820da4c7f26278bf99c224a1","tid":296830,"uid":66659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:14:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老實講 你呢個價錢留返d錢租琴房鍊最實際<br />\n彈電子琴手感唔同好易彈壞手<br />\n一係儲多d買R牌數碼琴啦</blockquote><br />\n要多幾錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新手想彈但係冇位擺琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前有去琴房練，但係覺得好貴先想買琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你同我個時一樣 <br />\n我個時日日收工成身汗咁走去琴行日日鍊兩個鐘<br />\n之後諗左好耐下定決心就去買左部Yamaha u1<br />\nR牌琴你預起碼一萬尾到 你可以去柏斯睇下試下琴試下聲同手感 鑽石山荷里活個間都幾大下 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我屋企冇位擺， 所以唔可以買直立式果D琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以以為細部嘅琴平D<br />\n其實新手都係想試下電子琴<br />\n所以買部質素中間D嘅琴試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d0cfee84d948a518e504b4eade4df49934dc06","tid":296830,"uid":102224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:15:59.000Z","msg":"我都係新開，買左p225<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d83d173a424df2d